The closed set of in-scope EssilorLuxottica-owned or licensed eyewear brands for this task:
{=% for canonical, aliases in brand_aliases.items() =%}
- **{= canonical =}**{= " (also known as: " + (aliases | join(", ")) + ")" if aliases else "" =}
